name: Tyra Banks
description:
Tyra Lynne Banks (born December 4, 1973), also known as BanX, is an American television personality, model, producer, writer, and actress.

Trained on 1.5 base model but examples are from Analog Madness and Consistent Factor

Skews heavily "forehead" (that is amongst the oddest sentences I have written today), but all pictures were SFW public photos from 1997 to 2008 period

This is the first non playboy model i have built(though it is a shame she never posed for them)

I'm not 100% sure on the version of the checkpoint i like best. This is the 1200 step version. The 2000 was overcooked, but please let me know if you have any feedback, particularly on this model.
